## table card | doc="A card instance. phase categorises flow-bound value cards (triage/active/terminal); defaults 'active' for non-value cards (the value is unused there)."

### meta
name_attribute, id_column
title, id

### columns
name, type, pk, nullable, default, references, on_delete
id, bigserial, true, false, , ,
card_type_id, bigint, false, false, , card_type.id, restrict
parent_card_id, bigint, false, true, , card.id, cascade
phase, text, false, false, 'active', ,
deleted_at, timestamptz, false, true, , ,


